- Categorization is based on the sequence of access dates and the corresponding Treasury Bill series; 
- The data only includes entries from June 2023, indicating a focus on a specific time frame for the analysis; 
- The inclusion of yield curve data and auction details suggests a comprehensive analysis aiming to relate Treasury Bill data to broader market trends and user access patterns.

